rComments: Great instructor overall! Lectures were interesting. Lots of readings though and you do really have to take detailed notes on them. The quizzes were difficult, as was the exam, but youll be fine if you stay on top of the content and take good notes.
teacherRatingTags: ['Beware of pop quizzes', 'Get ready to read', "Skip class? You won't pass."]

rComments: Prof Spicier was a great professor for GGR339. His lectures were interesting and engaging. The quizzes were a bit difficult because they were fill-in-the-blank but they weren't worth much. Final wasn't bad either. Nothing unexpected from the course. It's a great course to sit back and really take in the information. + Prof. Spicier is hilarious!
